about.summary: Data used as examples to demonstrate GAMLSS models.

name: r-gamlss.data
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set version = '5.1-4' %}
{% set posix = 'm2-' if win else '' %}
{% set native = 'm2w64-' if win else '' %}

package:
  name: r-gamlss.data
  version: {{ version|replace("-", "_") }}

source:
  url:
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/gamlss.data_{{ version }}.tar.gz
    - {{ cran_mirror }}/src/contrib/Archive/gamlss.data/gamlss.data_{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: 0d3777d8c3cd76cef273aa6bde40a91688719be401195ed9bfd1e85bd7d5eeb5

build:
  merge_build_host: True  # [win]
  number: 2
  noarch: generic
  rpaths:
    - lib/R/lib/
    - lib/

requirements:
  build:
    - {{ posix }}zip               # [win]
  host:
    - r-base
  run:
    - r-base

test:
  commands:
    - $R -e "library('gamlss.data')"           # [not win]
    - "\"%R%\" -e \"library('gamlss.data')\""  # [win]

about:
  home: http://www.gamlss.org/
  license: GPL-2 | GPL-3
  summary: Data used as examples to demonstrate GAMLSS models.
  license_family: GPL3
  license_file: '{{ environ["PREFIX"] }}/lib/R/share/licenses/GPL-2'

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - conda-forge/r
